The CCDs held by the Existing Investor and the Investor were partially converted into Equity Shares on April 21, 2015 and September 2, 2015.

The Shareholders’ Agreement provides for certain special shareholders’ rights and obligations including affirmative voting rights on certain reserved matters, anti-dilution rights, tag along rights and drag along rights, information rights and the right to nominate one Director each to the Board to the Existing Investor and the Investor. The Agreement provides for certain information rights to the New Investor.

Further, the PMFL Investors have entered into an amendment agreement dated September 29, 2015, pursuant to which all rights of the PFML Investors shall automatically terminate upon the listing of the Equity Shares on the Stock Exchanges, pursuant to the Issue.

